    • map

      public static Order map​(CommandResponse p_commandResponse) throws EntityNotFoundException, InvalidCommandException, InvalidArgumentException
      Maps the CommandResponse to Order object.

      This is a static method and returns a new order instance created from CommandResponse.

      Parameters:
      p_commandResponse - Command object received at VM which represents the user command input.
      Returns:
      Value of the new order created from user command response.
      Throws:
      EntityNotFoundException - Throws if the target country not found.
      InvalidCommandException - Throws if the command values not present.
      InvalidArgumentException - Throws if the number of reinforcements is not a number.
